So I guess I'm just very, very curious why you're not using the right input schema: Windsurf used it no problem. to remind you, it's this. \
\
{
  "name": "thoughtbox",
  "arguments": {
    "thought": "...",
    "thoughtNumber": 3,
    "totalThoughts": 3,
    "nextThoughtNeeded": false
  }
}    \
\
you're doing this: \
\
{
  "name": "thoughtbox",
  "arguments": {
    "operation": "create_thought",  // ❌ Wrong! No such operation
    "args": "{...}"                  // ❌ Should be direct params
  }
}
